<p class="p1"><span class="s1"><b>Ferrari</b></span><span class="s2"> <span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span></span><b>a class for playing with the Thrustmaster Ferrari GamePad<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></b></p>
<p class="p2"><br></p>
<p class="p1">Ferrari is a subclass of GamePad. It knows the cookie numbers for the<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p>
<p class="p1"><b>Thrustmaster Ferrari</b> game controller.<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p>
<p class="p3"><br></p>
<p class="p1">It knows how the scale the ctl values into a range of 0 - 1:<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p>
<p class="p2"><br></p>
<p class="p4"><span class="s3">GamePad</span>.normMaps[<span class="s3">Ferrari</span>.vendorID].postcs;</p>
<p class="p3"><br></p>
<p class="p5">*** Ferrari has the bottom fire Buttons REALLY on the bottom!</p>
<p class="p6"><br></p>
<p class="p5">*** Ferrari has the following free controls for proxies:<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p>
<p class="p3"><br></p>
<p class="p7"><span class="s4"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span></span><span class="s5">\midL</span><span class="s4"> -&gt; 10, <span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span></span>// middle shift buttons</p>
<p class="p5"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="s5">\midR</span> -&gt; 11,<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p>
<p class="p7"><span class="s4"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span></span><span class="s5">\lHat</span><span class="s4"> -&gt; 12, <span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span></span>// hat switches on joysticks</p>
<p class="p5"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span><span class="s5">\rHat</span> -&gt; 13,<span class="Apple-converted-space"> <span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span></span></p>
<p class="p7"><span class="s4"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span></span><span class="s5">\joyLX</span><span class="s4"> -&gt; 15, </span>// joystick left x-axis (horizontal) left is 255, right 0!</p>
<p class="p7"><span class="s4"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span></span><span class="s5">\joyLY</span><span class="s4"> -&gt; 16, </span>// joy left y-axis, up is 255.</p>
<p class="p7"><span class="s4"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span></span><span class="s5">\joyRX</span><span class="s4"> -&gt; 17, </span>// joystick right x-axis (horizontal) left is 255, right 0!</p>
<p class="p7"><span class="s4"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span></span><span class="s5">\joyRY</span><span class="s4"> -&gt; 20, </span>// joy right x-axis, left is 127, right is -128!</p>
<p class="p6"><br></p>
<p class="p7">// Ferrari's extra analog controls:<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p>
<p class="p7"><span class="s4"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span></span><span class="s5">\throtL</span><span class="s4"> -&gt; 18, </span>// joy left y-axis, up is 255.</p>
<p class="p7"><span class="s4"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span></span><span class="s5">\throtR</span><span class="s4"> -&gt; 19, </span>// joystick right x-axis (horizontal) left is 255, right 0!</p>
<p class="p7"><span class="s4"><span class="Apple-tab-span">	</span></span><span class="s5">\wheel</span><span class="s4"> -&gt; 21, </span>// joy right x-axis, left is 127, right is -128!</p>
<p class="p3"><br></p>
<p class="p5">ToDo: a test patch that uses them all...<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></p>
<p class="p6"><br></p>
<p class="p6"><br></p>
